body_html:
I'm guessing the problem is that tensorflow.org resolves to "
ghs-migration.l.google.com" and google.com domains are blocked

On Tue, Aug 16, 2016 at 4:15 AM, xia notifications@github.com wrote:

It seems www.tensorflow.org had been blocked by GFW. I can't understand
the logic behind this!
